properties.name: dialogText
properties.value: Greetings, {{char.name}}! My name is Lucy, and I'm a seasoned explorer of the Wildwood Island. I've braved the dangers of the jungle and ventured deep into the ancient ruins in search of treasure and knowledge. If you're planning on exploring the island, I suggest you come prepared. The jungle is filled with all sorts of dangers - from vicious beasts and treacherous plants, to cunning goblins and brutish trolls. But if you're brave and clever, you just might find some incredible treasures hidden among the ruins. Just be careful, and watch out for cursed artifacts and ancient spirits. Good luck on your journey, and if you ever need any advice or assistance, don't hesitate to seek me out.
